thread.title: S. Cline

author: S. Cline
title: S. Cline
text: This was my first time using and trusting Opticontacts to deliver great products, low prices, and helpful customer service. I ordered my Biofinity Toric lenses with a prescription and had a smooth and seamless customer experience! The price for the contact lenses is the most competitive price I've found online, and trust me I did my research! Thank you to Opticontacts for delivering a great customer experience. Will definitely recommend to anyone looking for great products, pricing, and service.
